            But revolutions invite resistance.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-8">
            One by one, the big players began locking down the very festivals we worked with, 
            luring them back with buyouts and exclusivity.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-8">
            That could've been the end. But instead, we decided to evolve.
          </p>
        </div>
